law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 285, sec. 14; and amended ch. 315, sec. 14. -- Created 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 33.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Inspection of dam, embankment or levee -- Orders for remedy -- Judicial review -- Mandatory injunction.
metadata.lrc-note: . This section was amended by 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 315, sec. 14, which was part of a general amendatory act providing for certified mail delivery. It was specifically repealed by 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 285, sec. 14, which was passed last by the General Assembly and so stands, even though it was signed by the Governor on the same day.
